And so I don't know what the Lord has been doing in your soul as I've been speaking.

40:03.031 --> 40:16.824
I don't know if He's caught your attention in some way and revealed something inside of you that needs to change so that He can use you in the midst of somebody's pain.

40:16.884 --> 40:21.288
But if that's the case, I just want to ask you to ask Him for help.

40:21.308 --> 40:22.930
Take this moment now in quietness

40:23.394 --> 40:24.756
Ask him to mobilize you.

40:26.138 --> 40:35.429
Ask him to send you a page, a little beep, beep, beep, beep, and alert you to the needs that are in front of you.

40:36.471 --> 40:39.354
Ask him to open your eyes, to open your heart.

40:39.374 --> 40:41.617
Maybe there's a callousness that you've allowed to develop.

40:43.860 --> 40:51.570
Ask him to take those callous areas off and strip your heart into a place of humility to help you to see

40:52.290 --> 40:54.573
A fresh and be affected by people's pain.

40:56.896 --> 40:58.338
Ask him to help you with your focus.

41:00.801 --> 41:02.183
So take this moment now and go to him.

41:03.865 --> 41:06.528
Ask him for help and then I'll pray for you as we close.

41:14.538 --> 41:18.123
God, I thank you for your church, for your people.

41:19.725 --> 41:20.786
Called out ones.

41:21.378 --> 41:25.223
Sanctified, set apart, bought with the precious blood of the Lamb.

41:26.664 --> 41:30.529
And sometimes, Lord, we find ourselves in places that we grow callous and cold.

41:30.609 --> 41:35.275
So God, I ask that you would just speak to my heart.

41:36.837 --> 41:37.758
Help me to see God.

41:38.199 --> 41:38.879
Help me to feel.

41:38.939 --> 41:50.834
Help me to know when you're calling me to intercept somebody's need and step in as an extension of your hand into our lives.

41:51.010 --> 41:51.751
into their lives.

41:53.153 --> 41:55.716
Lord, would you do the same for my brothers and sisters in this room tonight?

41:56.497 --> 41:58.880
God, we want to be people motivated by you.

42:00.001 --> 42:01.604
We want to be people moved by you.

42:03.146 --> 42:10.074
God, we want to be an extension of your mighty right arm at a time when people need it most.

42:11.356 --> 42:19.186
So help us God to get rid of excuses and move from a place of comfort and straight into compassion, especially in

42:19.746 --> 42:25.032
This season, God of Thanksgiving and Christmas, there will be needs all around us.

42:26.613 --> 42:27.795
So would you God deploy us?

42:28.475 --> 42:30.057
Would you deploy us to be your agents?

42:30.858 --> 42:36.123
Would you deploy this church to be change makers in South Florida?

42:36.143 --> 42:46.194
Would you deploy the churches that call themselves a part of church united to be agents, change makers for your kingdom and for your glory?

42:46.562 --> 42:48.104
Together, God, we want to see you move.

42:48.144 --> 42:50.086
We want to see your name made famous.

42:50.566 --> 42:52.528
We want to see your revival here in South Florida.

42:53.069 --> 42:57.173
So you got to be repent of ways that allow us to be cold.

42:58.275 --> 43:04.281
We repent God of inaction and pray, God, would you make us men and women of action?

43:04.341 --> 43:09.006
Help us God to do this by your will, for your glory and for your purposes.

43:09.587 --> 43:12.530
And we pray this in Jesus' name, amen.

43:16.770 --> 43:18.514
Thanks for listening to today's message.

43:19.295 --> 43:23.303
Here at Calvary, we believe a relationship with Jesus changes everything.

43:23.323 --> 43:30.538
And if you've decided to follow Jesus, we'd love for you to text the word believe to 31352 so you can find out what it means to follow Christ.

43:31.340 --> 43:36.530
And to learn more about Calvary and all of our campuses, you're free to visit calvaryftl.org.

